s can see analytics.'=>'Awọn ipa olumulo ti a yan nikan ni wọn le ri awọn iṣiro.','Who Can Control Settings'=>'Tani Le Ṣakoso Eto','Only selected user roles can control settings.'=>'Awọn ipa olumulo ti a yan nikan ni wọn le ṣakoso awọn eto.','Auto-Linking'=>'Akọsílẹ-Auto','Enable Auto-Linking'=>'Mú Akọsílẹ-Auto ṣiṣẹ','Automatically convert keywords to shortlinks in post content.'=>'Yipada awọn bọtini ọrọ si awọn ọna asopọ kekeke laifọwọyi ninu akoonu ifiweranṣẹ.','When enabled, keywords configured in shortlink settings will be automatically linked in your content.'=>'Nigbati a ba mu ṣiṣẹ, awọn bọtini ọrọ ti a ṣeto ninu awọn eto ọna asopọ kekeke yoo jẹ asopọ laifọwọyi ninu akoonu rẹ.','Open Auto-Links In'=>'Ṣii Awọn Aso-Akọsílẹ Ni','Choose how auto-linked keywords should open.'=>'Yan bi awọn bọtini ọrọ ti a so pọ yẹ ki o ṣii.','Same tab'=>'Tẹ́ńbá àtàwọn','New tab'=>'Tẹ́ńbá tuntun','Auto-Link Color'=>'Àwọ̀ Akọsílẹ-Auto','Choose the color for auto-linked keywords.'=>'Yan awọ fun awọn bọtini ọrọ ti a so pọ.','Auto-List Links'=>'Akọsílẹ-Auto Línkì','Auto-List Shortlinks'=>'Akọsílẹ-Auto Kekèké Línkì','When enabled, shortlinks will appear in the "All Links" table based on the behavior you configure below.'=>'Nigbati o ba ti mu ṣiṣẹ, awọn ọna asopọ kukuru yoo han ninu tabili "Gbogbo Awọn ọna asopọ" da lori ihuwasi ti o ṣeto ni isalẹ.','Configure Post Types'=>'Configure Post Types','Set when links should be auto-listed for each post type'=>'Ṣeto nigbati awọn ọna asopọ yẹ ki o wa ni akojọ laifọwọyi fun ọkọọkan post type','Add post types and configure when their shortlinks should appear in the "All Links" table. Changes are saved automatically.'=>'Fikun un post types ki o si ṣeto nigbati awọn ọna asopọ kukuru wọn yẹ ki o han ninu tabili "Gbogbo Awọn ọna asopọ". Awọn ayipada ni a fipamọ laifọwọyi.','Post Status Visibility'=>'Post Status Visibility','Allowed Post Statuses'=>'Allowed Post Statuses','Choose which post statuses can be accessed via shortlinks'=>'Yan iru awọn ipo ifiweranṣẹ ti o le wọle nipasẹ awọn ọna asopọ kukuru','Published'=>'Ti a tẹjade','Draft'=>'Iwe afọwọkọ','Pending Review'=>'N duro de Atunwo','Private'=>'Ikọkọ','Expired Links'=>'Awọn ọna asopọ ti pari','Default Expired Redirect URL'=>'URL Atunṣe ti o pari aiyipada','Where should expired shortlinks redirect?'=>'Nibo ni awọn ọna asopọ kukuru ti o pari yẹ ki o tọka si?','When a shortlink expires, visitors will be redirected to this URL instead of seeing an error. Leave empty to show the default expiration message.'=>'Nigbati ọna asopọ kukuru ba pari, awọn alejo yoo tọka si URL yii dipo ki o ri aṣiṣe kan. Fi silẹ lati fi ifiranṣẹ ipari aiyipada han.','Revisions'=>'Revisions','Revision Link Visibility'=>'Ihuwasi Asọye Atunṣe','When enabled, revision shortlinks will appear in the "All Shortlinks" table based on the behavior you configure below.'=>'Nigbati o ba ti mu ṣiṣẹ, awọn ọna asopọ kukuru atunṣe yoo han ninu tabili "Gbogbo Awọn ọna asopọ kukuru" da lori ihuwasi ti o ṣeto ni isalẹ.','When Revision is Created'=>'Nigbati Atunṣe ba ti ṣẹda','When Revision is Created or Link is First Used'=>'Nigbati Atunṣe ba ti ṣẹda tabi ọna asopọ ti wa ni lilo akọkọ','Show Shortlink in Revision Table'=>'Fihan Shortlink ninu Iwe Atunyẹwo','Display shortlink column when viewing revisions in PublishPress Revisions.'=>'Fihan àkọsílẹ shortlink nigba ti o n wo awọn atunṣe ni PublishPress Revisions.','Revision Visibility for Visitors'=>'Ifarahan Atunyẹwo fun Awọn Alejo','Allow logged-out visitors to view revision content via shortlinks.'=>'Jẹ ki awọn alejo ti ko wọlé wo akoonu atunṣe nipasẹ shortlinks.','By default, PublishPress Revisions blocks visitors from viewing revision previews. When enabled, revision shortlinks will render the revision content directly for logged-out visitors instead of redirecting to the preview URL.'=>'Ni aiyipada, PublishPress Revisions dènà awọn alejo lati wo awọn ayẹwo atunṣe. Nigba ti a ba mu un ṣiṣẹ, awọn shortlinks atunṣe yoo ṣe afihan akoonu atunṣe taara fun awọn alejo ti ko wọlé dipo ti yí wọn lọ si URL ayẹwo.','Dummy'=>'Dummy','No post types configured yet. Click "Add Post Type" to get started.'=>'Ko si awọn iru post ti a ti ṣeto sibẹsibẹ. Tẹ "Fi Iru Post Kún" lati bẹrẹ.','Add Post Type'=>'Fi Iru Post Kún','Log entry deleted successfully.'=>'Iwé àkọọlẹ ti pa ni aṣeyọri.','%d log entries deleted successfully.'=>'%d iwe àkọọlẹ ti pa ni aṣeyọri.','All logs have been cleared.'=>'Gbogbo awọn iwe àkọọlẹ ti wa ni mimọ.','Title'=>'Àkọlé','Details'=>'Àlàyé','Are you sure you want to delete this log entry?'=>'Ṣe o dájú pe o fẹ pa iwe àkọọlẹ yii?','Tablet'=>'Tablet','Mobile'=>'Mobile','Desktop'=>'Desktop','%1$s from %2$s visited at %3$s'=>'%1$s lati %2$s ṣabẹwo ni %3$s','%1$s visited at %2$s'=>'%1$s ṣabẹwo ni %2$s','From %1$s, visited at %2$s'=>'Lati %1$s, ṣabẹwo ni %2$s','Visited at %s'=>'Ti a ṣàbẹwò ni %s','via %s'=>'nipasẹ %s','Edit shortlink settings'=>'Ṣatunkọ eto asopọ kukuru','Target url not found.'=>'URL ibi ti a ń fẹ ko ri.','Invalid URL scheme. Only http, https, ftp, ftps, and mailto are allowed.'=>'Ilana URL ti ko tọ. Nikan http, https, ftp, ftps, ati mailto ni a gba laaye.','Invalid URL.'=>'URL ti ko tọ.','Tiny slug could not created.'=>'A ko le ṣẹda slug kekere.','Link - %s'=>'Asopọ - %s','Shortlink will appear here'=>'Asopọ kukuru yoo han nibi','Enter a long URL and make a shortlink'=>'Tẹ URL gigun kan ki o ṣẹda asopọ kukuru','Long URL'=>'URL Gigun','Close'=>'Pa','Create Shortlink'=>'Ṣẹda Asopọ Kukuru','Reset Today\'s Analytics'=>'Tun Analytics Ọjọ́ Tó Rẹ́ Sọ́kan','Reset Week\'s Analytics'=>'Tun Analytics Ọsẹ́ Tó Rẹ́ Sọ́kan','Reset Month\'s Analytics'=>'Tun Analytics Oṣù Tó Rẹ́ Sọ́kan','Reset Year\'s Analytics'=>'Tun Analytics Ọdún Tó Rẹ́ Sọ́kan','Are you sure you want to reset the analytics for this period? This action cannot be undone.'=>'Ṣé o dájú pé o fẹ́ tun awọn analytics fun akoko yii? Iṣe yii ko le pada sẹhin.','Today'=>'Loni','Last 7 Days'=>'Ọjọ́ 7 Tó Kẹhin','Last 1 Month'=>'Oṣù 1 to kẹhin','Last 1 Year'=>'Ọdún 1 to kẹhin','If you like %1$s please leave us a %2$s rating. Thank you!'=>'Ti o ba fẹ %1$s jọwọ fi wa %2$s ìdíyelé. Ẹ ṣé!','About'=>'Nipa','Documentation'=>'Iwe aṣẹ','Contact'=>'Kan si','Download QR Code'=>'Gba Koodu QR','We have developed extensions for the below browsers.'=>'A ti ṣe idagbasoke awọn afikun fun awọn aṣawakiri ti o wa ni isalẹ.','Click on your preferred one to Download the extension.'=>'Tẹ lori ọkan ti o fẹ lati Gba afikun naa.','Download the Extension'=>'Gba afikun naa','Need PublishPress Shortlinks Support?'=>'Nilo Atilẹyin PublishPress Shortlinks?','If you need help or have a new feature request, let us know.'=>'Ti o ba nilo iranlọwọ tabi ni ibeere ẹya tuntun, jẹ ki a mọ.','Request Support'=>'Beere Atilẹyin','Detailed documentation is also available on the plugin website.'=>'Iwe aṣẹ alaye tun wa lori oju opo wẹẹbu plugin naa.','View Knowledge Base'=>'Wo Ibi ìmọ','This plugin can be deleted.'=>'A le pa plugin yii run.','Copied.'=>'Ti a daakọ.']];